M5Stack StickS3 (m5stack_sticks3/esp32s3/procpu) - HW-003 LCD evidence
Captured: 2026-05-30 via esp-idf-monitor on Windows COM9.

LCD: ST7789P3 (135x240) on SPI2 via zephyr,mipi-dbi-spi; x-offset=52, y-offset=40,
inversion ON, RGB565, 40 MHz. Power rail unlocked by the new M5PM1 PMIC regulator
driver (drivers/regulator/regulator_m5pm1.c) driving M5PM1 GPIO2 (PYG2) high (L3B).

Visual confirmation (user, 2026-05-30): the panel cycles solid colors
red -> green -> blue -> white once per second (the app's fill_screen test).

Serial heartbeat confirms display init succeeded ("disp=ready" every line):

